         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The material in the original accession is arranged chronologically, with photographs last. Additions to the collection may vary in arrangement.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_ef8c85154f1044f48888096f3529980d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of printed material relating to current political, economic, and social conditions in Cameroon. Also included are photographs.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
